{"id": 851, "genre": 1001, "title": "你觉得新时代的孝心到底体现在哪？", "description": "我远程教我妈用app store下东西的时候一次脾气都没有发，我真是世界第一好儿子。（题图来自：Dahu·Wang）", "record_count": 3605, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160703181345jfeVJ2xm3KWdpstC.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-03-06T01:00:51Z", "options": [{"id": 56064, "content": "不跟他们吵架。", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 343696}, {"id": 56065, "content": "太多了，這頁紙不夠寫！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 458051}, {"id": 56066, "content": "陪陪伴", "image": null, "praise_count": 31, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 159748}, {"id": 55555, "content": "帮我爸妈记着他们的QQ、微信、微博、银行账户各种密码", "image": null, "praise_count": 224, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 56069, "content": "父母面前不玩手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 371344}, {"id": 56325, "content": "陪伴/聊天", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 452911}, {"id": 55558, "content": "帮我妈网购", "image": null, "praise_count": 235, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 55559, "content": "帮家长清理电脑，与360作斗争", "image": null, "praise_count": 171, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 56071, "content": "不让他们担心，对他们时常关心！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 433370}, {"id": 56072, "content": "对爸妈发的心灵鸡汤每次都认真看", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 315651}, {"id": 57608, "content": "陪父母多聊聊天", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 502468}, {"id": 56329, "content": "帮妈妈拍照好像游击队一样扑倒在地", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 103167}, {"id": 56585, "content": "耐心对他们", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 486219}, {"id": 56074, "content": "陪妈妈逛超市，坚持每天打电话陪妈妈聊天。", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 504655}, {"id": 56075, "content": "把排版变成以前那种吧……现在的真难受", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 250405}, {"id": 74252, "content": "别老是嚷嚷“说走就走”，带上爸妈吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 595067}, {"id": 56076, "content": "1.删掉他们所有的微信公众号，把我关注的公众号强行推荐给他们。2.在解答有关电子设备使用方面的问题时保持全程不发脾气。3.反驳他们时不做出鄙夷和高高在上的姿态。不过我一次都没做到过，总以吵架收场……", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 73406}, {"id": 56077, "content": "耐心听她们的唠叨", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 498530}, {"id": 56080, "content": "给我妈美颜", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 42062}, {"id": 58128, "content": "回去多陪陪他们，而不是单纯的物质给予", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 467049}, {"id": 56081, "content": "以及多赚钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 168505}, {"id": 56082, "content": "悦活且真正的爱自己，不让父母为我们担心。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 403291}, {"id": 56084, "content": "教我妈怎样发朋友圈有逼格，让她成为同代大妈种的朋友圈杀手XD", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 456926}, {"id": 56086, "content": "多打电话，多抽时间回家看看", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 482898}, {"id": 56087, "content": "教长辈学会发红包！", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 463104}, {"id": 56088, "content": "在爸妈面前不一直玩手机抢红包", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 493344}, {"id": 56346, "content": "陪伴，不想他们老去", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 506191}, {"id": 56093, "content": "给妈妈买护肤品买靓靓的衣服等  给爸爸买帅帅衣服等 买营养品", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 184671}, {"id": 56094, "content": "找到女朋友……我真是不孝", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 91804}, {"id": 56095, "content": "陪父母吃早饭", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 59213}, {"id": 56351, "content": "陪伴。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 506219}, {"id": 56096, "content": "  愿意让他们了解你的生活圈 愿意和他们交流", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 504714}, {"id": 61216, "content": "每天回家都要给妈妈个拥抱", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 531071}, {"id": 56097, "content": "每天与父母一个电话，坚持10年。", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 495533}, {"id": 56098, "content": "首先要自己过得好 让父母不用担心 然后多陪陪他们 无论是常回家看看 还是多打打电话 让他们感觉到温暖 首先是这两个精神层面上 要让他们觉得轻松 无压力 然后才是生活水平上 尽力提高 定期带父母去体检 身体最重要 让他们吃穿住用行都舒服 当然这一点我们无法左右 他们可能过惯了以前的日子 我们让他们做出改变恐怕不适应 当然 我是从一个农村出来的女儿对父母爱的表达", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 488810}, {"id": 56354, "content": "一起旅游", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 506152}, {"id": 56867, "content": "和家人在一起，不玩手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 83110}, {"id": 56100, "content": "夸妈妈织的毛衣好看！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 181495}, {"id": 56102, "content": "少让他们担心", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 423430}, {"id": 56358, "content": "陪家人的时候不玩手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 306692}, {"id": 56103, "content": "什么时代爸妈都需要陪在身边，而不是存在手机里", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 503875}, {"id": 56104, "content": "自己能照顾好自己。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 457970}, {"id": 56616, "content": " 我就在家，并且父母没有微信，这可能是最孝顺的人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 507235}, {"id": 56105, "content": "记得时刻关心他们☺️有什么好玩好吃好看的不忘给他们带一份?‍?‍?", "image": "img/option/option/20160702182639c2YAoitjTzrpSBR3.jpg", "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 239957}, {"id": 56106, "content": "陪父母吃饭、聊天、看电视、旅游、教他们网购，尽量少发脾气，常保持?，不让他们担心。我觉得最大的孝心就是陪伴。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 500095}, {"id": 56107, "content": "每个星期总会饮次茶", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 504809}, {"id": 56108, "content": "和家里人吃饭，不看手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 460896}, {"id": 56110, "content": "不要让爸妈再伤心了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 343696}, {"id": 56111, "content": "嫁人…虽然我没这个想法", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 428778}, {"id": 56112, "content": "给生活费或是零花钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 504847}]}